FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS
Hidden element
Are reservations required?
Due to our unique size, we currently do not offer reservations. We apologize for any inconvenience.
Do you offer Happy Hour?
Yes, we offer Happy Hour Monday through Friday from 2PM – 6PM. View our menu
here
.
Do you only serve beer?
We offer a full liquor bar including your favorite beers as well as  wine by the glass.
Where are you located?
Tucked away on Park Avenue, ABO is located in Winter Park’s Hidden Garden, behind Boca.
Do you offer non-seafood options?
Yes, in addition to our fresh seafood, our menu includes items to please non–seafood lovers as well.
